"3/4 cup fresh Key lime juice (about 36 Key limes)","1 cup granulated sugar","1/4 cup cornstarch","3 large egg yolks","2 large eggs","7 tablespoons (3 1/2 oz.) unsalted butter","2 cups heavy cream","1 (8-oz.) pkg.  cream cheese, at room temperature","1/2 cup (about 2 oz.) powdered sugar","2 teaspoons Key lime zest, plus more for garnish (about 4 Key limes)","6 (6-oz.) pkg.  shortbread cookies (such as Walkers Shortbread)","1 1/4 cups cups roasted unsalted pistachios, finely chopped"